right thing to do.


163
00:09:13,226 --> 00:09:16,926
So, let's take a made-up
example to illustrate a point.


164
00:09:17,506 --> 00:09:20,606
This is for a fictitious
hair salon and make


165
00:09:20,606 --> 00:09:21,886
up studio called Fuzz.


